    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Equipment (bits, bridal, chest piece, forehead fringe, halters, headstalls, neck pieces, saddles, headstalls, neck pieces, saddles, saddle blankets, etc.) used on a horse, particularly when the equipment is decorative.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047060/National Museum of African Art Library (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Decoratieve uitrusting (bit, hoofdstel, #borstplaat, #hoofdfranje, halster, kopstuk, #nekstuk, zadel, zadeldeken, enzovoort) waarmee een paard wordt opgetuigd.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Schmückende Ausrüstung (Trense, Zaumzeug, Brustplatte, Stirnbesatz, Halfter, Zaumzeug, Halsplatte, Sattel, Satteldecke usw.), die bei einem Pferd verwendet wird.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>馬身上的裝飾設備（馬勒、轡頭、胸部裝飾、額頭流穗、韁繩、絡頭、頸部裝飾、馬鞍、頭部裝飾、馬鞍毯等）。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
